posting_body: ['Welcome Home', 'Welcome to Ironwood Apartments, where quality and comfort meet.', 'Located in the heart of Livermore CA, our apartment homes offer the perfect combination of wine country charm, distinctive details, and convenience in an unparalleled location.', 'Relax at home, entertain your guests and take advantage of the quality amenities that are designed to enhance your living experience.', 'If you are in the mood for exploring, reach San Jose or San Francisco and discover the best dining, shopping, and recreation the nearby cities have to offer.', 'Your options are endless at Ironwood Apartments!', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'x 1', 'OR Text', '1', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to text our leasing team.', 'Want more information on this unit?', 'See link (below):', '<URL>', 'This is a 2 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 796 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Features', '- Stainless Steel Appliances', '- Ceiling Fans with Lighting', '- Plank Vinyl Flooring', '- One-, Two- and Three-Bedroom Residences', '- Plush Carpeting', '- Personal Patios or Balconies', '- Custom Window Coverings', '- Complete Appliance Package*', '- Open-Concept Living Spaces', '- In-Home Washer and Dryer', 'Community Amenities', '- Complete Fitness Center', '- We Love Pets!*', '- Online Payments, Leasing and Customer Service Requests', '- Reserved Covered Parking*', '- Community Barbecues', '- Guest Parking Available', '- Playground', '- Online Payments Available', '- Resort-Inspired Pool', '- Clothes-Care Facility', '- Lush Landscaping', 'Pet Policy', 'We love your pets!', 'Please contact us for more information and details.', 'Office Hours', 'Monday-Saturday:10:30AM-4:30PM', 'Ironwood', '5643 Charlotte Way, Livermore, CA, 94550', '1PMJedD3olWy']
